 UEFA Cup Winners' Cup#Qualifying round|Cup Winners' Cup qualifying round]]\n|col_UC1Q=blue1  |text_UC1Q=Qualification for the [[1997\u201398 UEFA Cup#First qualifying round|UEFA Cup first qualifying round]]\n|col_REL=red1    |text_REL=Relegation to the [[1997\u201398 Macedonian Second Football League|Macedonian Second League]]\n|note_res_CWCQ= Since [[FK Sileks|Sileks]], winners of [[1996\u201397 Macedonian Football Cup]], was qualified for the [[1997\u201398 UEFA Champions League]], losing cup finalists [[FK Sloga Jugomagnat|Sloga Jugomagnat]] earned a spot in the [[1997\u201398 UEFA Cup Winners' Cup#Qualifying round|qualifying round]] of the 1997\u201398 UEFA Cup Winners' Cup.\n\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Results==\n{{#invoke:sports results|main\n|matches_style=FBR\n|team1=BAL|team2=BEL|team3=BRE|team4=CEM|team5=MGP\n|team6=PEL|team7=POB|team8=RUD|team9=SAS|team10=SKE\n|team11=SIL|team12=SLO|team13=TIK|team14=VAR\n\n|name_BAL=[[FK Balkan Skopje|Balkan]]\n|match_BAL_BEL=4\u20131\n|match_BAL_BRE=3\u20130\n|match_BAL_CEM=2\u20130\n|match_BAL_MGP=2\u20131\n|match_BAL_PEL=2\u20132\n|match_BAL_POB=1\u20132\n|match_BAL_RUD=2\u20131\n|match_BAL_SAS=0\u20130\n|match_BAL_SKE=0\u20130\n|match_BAL_SIL=4\u20131\n|match_BAL_SLO=1\u20130\n|match_BAL_TIK=2\u20134\n|match_BAL_VAR=0\u20130\n\n|name_BEL=[[FK Belasica|Belasica]]\n|match_BEL_BAL=2\u20131\n|match_BEL_BRE=1\u20131\n|match_BEL_CEM=3\u20131\n|match_BEL_MGP=1\u20130\n|match_BEL_PEL=1\u20131\n|match_BEL_POB=1\u20132\n|match_BEL_RUD=4\u20130\n|match_BEL_SAS=1\u20130\n|match_BEL_SKE=3\u20130\n|match_BEL_SIL=0\u20130\n|match_BEL_SLO=1\u20131\n|match_BEL_TIK=1\u20131\n|match_BEL_VAR=1\u20130\n\n|name_BRE=[[FK Bregalnica \u0160tip|Bregalnica Shtip]]\n|match_BRE_BAL=2\u20131\n|match_BRE_BEL=2\u20131\n|match_BRE_CEM=2\u20130\n|match_BRE_MGP=2\u20131\n|match_BRE_PEL=1\u20130\n|match_BRE_POB=0\u20131\n|match_BRE_RUD=8\u20130\n|match_BRE_SAS=0\u20130\n|match_BRE_SKE=3\u20130\n|match_BRE_SIL=1\u20131\n|match_BRE_SLO=0\u20132\n|match_BRE_